== Post-COVID ME/CFS
<sec:post-covid-debates>

The COVID-19 pandemic created the largest wave of post-viral illness in modern history, with an estimated 51% of long COVID patients meeting PEM criteria also satisfying ME/CFS diagnostic criteria @Komaroff2023. This overlap has profoundly affected both the ME/CFS and long COVID fields.

